   * This project requires the following environment:
   * - Node.js >= 18.17.0 (Next.js 14 requirement)
   * - npm >= 9.6.0
   * 
   * Critical dependencies:
   * - Next.js 14.x: Core framework (requires Node.js >= 18.17.0)
   * - React 18.x: UI library
