   *   - markdown-to-jsx/react-markdown: For rendering legacy Markdown content
   *
   * When updating dependencies:
   * 1. Always update related packages together (e.g., all React packages)
   * 2. Test thoroughly after updates, especially content rendering
   * 3. Keep dependencies in sync with Node.js version requirements
   */
  
